{"tid":467641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大中華反港獨老屈梁天琦壹傳媒中期虧損擴大！ 蝕1.71億元！","createTime":"2017-11-13T16:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T05:05:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"03db086411cf7a51f2d62ab33a8031f563aaa6c4","tid":467641,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171113/57454654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57454654&d=RPK1G0yWOc9aoPi5Txb6Zv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5df8491f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171113%2F57454654&h=68ff9f50\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171113/57454654</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171113/large/1510577219_cc77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171113%2Flarge%2F1510577219_cc77.jpg&h=da81c368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒（282）公佈截至9月底止中期業績，收益為7.75億元，按年跌17%；期內虧損擴大至1.71億元。每股基本虧損7仙，不派息。虧損擴大主要由於港台市場低迷、廣告支出謹慎，加上線上程序化廣告購買面對全球激烈競爭。同時集團行重組程序，裁減報刊員工，產生代通知金810萬元，去年同期為3780萬元。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒最大收來源報章出版及印刷業務，由於廣告收益及發行收入顯著下跌，該業務跌18%至3.37億元，虧損擴大至7590萬元。《蘋果日報》收益跌兩成至1.41億元。首6個月每日平均銷量為12.4萬份，按年跌15%。《台灣蘋果日報》收益亦跌15%至1.95億元。<br />\n<br />\n數碼業務亦由盈轉虧，由於營運成本沉重，期內蝕2290萬元；收入跌12%至2.94億元。《蘋果日報》電子平台的外部收益下降，主要由於主要類別的廣告開支減少，廣告費用因業內程序化購買激增，而受到重大影響。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒不斷發掘新收入來源，將為市場引入iBeacon服務，根據智能手機地理位置定位提供資訊，為本地企業及活動提供資訊及廣告。集團指，繼續控制成本、改善工作流程效率、重組和精簡管理及營運程序，更於業績公告中提及「一帶一路」倡議重新整頓服務及消費行業經濟，為傳媒行業掀開全新機遇，已為此準備推出新產品和服務，擴闊收入來源。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">因果報應！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2272899b3410936d3254f4616e7882db12bd15e3","tid":467641,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"市值(港元) 11.917 億<br />\n<br />\n6年內玩完！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}